name: Get Startup Impact
description:
. Retrieves information of application impact on login process of last logged in user.  Result data is similar to the information in the Startup tab in Windows Task Manager, enhanced by detailed impact of each application. 

An issue related to Startup Impact measure was fixed by Microsoft in this [https://support. microsoft. com/en-us/topic/february-15-2022-kb5010415-os-builds-19042-1566-19043-1566-and-19044-1566-preview-5a644b82-83f4-4cc2-a0e7-85f643252386 KB]

inputs.description: Parameter is used to remove all processes matching provided name(s) from output. Multiple entries are separated by comma. Does not accept illegal characters. For more information see this [https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/windows/win32/fileio/naming-a-file article]
inputs.name: ApplicationsToExclude

outputs.description: User SID (Security Identifier) to whom the XML file containing the stats belongs
outputs.name: UserSID

outputs.description: Last time the startup information was updated on the device
outputs.name: LastStartUpAnalysisDate

outputs.description: Number of applications with a high startup impact
outputs.name: HighImpactCount

outputs.description: Details (CPU time in ms, Disk I/O in MB) of programs with a high startup impact
outputs.name: HighImpactApplications

outputs.description: Actionable names of programs with a high startup impact
outputs.name: HighImpactActionableApplications

outputs.description: Number of applications with a medium startup impact
outputs.name: MediumImpactCount

outputs.description: Details (CPU time in ms, Disk I/O in MB) of programs with a medium startup impact
outputs.name: MediumImpactApplications

outputs.description: Actionable names of programs with a medium startup impact
outputs.name: MediumImpactActionableApplications

outputs.description: Number of applications with a low startup impact
outputs.name: LowImpactCount

outputs.description: Details (CPU time in ms, Disk I/O in MB) of programs with a low startup impact
outputs.name: LowImpactApplications

outputs.description: Actionable names of programs with a low startup impact
outputs.name: LowImpactActionableApplications

outputs.description: Applications that were started but whose startup impacts were not measured by Microsoft Windows
outputs.name: NotMeasuredImpactApplications

outputs.description: Actionable names of programs not measured by Microsoft Windows
outputs.name: NotMeasuredImpactActionableApplications
